---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="bg-indigo-950 py-24 relative overflow-hidden" id="hidden-inflation">
    <!-- Background Texture -->
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 bg-[radial-gradient(#ffffff_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px]"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-center text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 via-purple-500 to-indigo-500 mb-20 uppercase tracking-tighter transform -rotate-2 drop-shadow-lg"
        >
            Los 4 Jinetes del <br class="md:hidden" /> "Apocalipsis del Súper"
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-8">
            <!-- 1. Reduflación -->
            <article
                class="group relative bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-800 hover:border-pink-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-2xl overflow-visible"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-6 -right-2 md:-right-6 rotate-12 bg-pink-600 text-white font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(219,39,119,0.4)] transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform z-20 border-2 border-pink-400"
                >
                    MENOS POR LO MISMO
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-pink-500/10 rounded-lg">
                        <Icon name="mdi:arrow-bottom-right-thick" class="w-8 h-8" />
                    </div>
                    Reduflación
                </h3>

                <div
                    class="h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-8 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-700 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(236,72,153,0.2)] transition-shadow"
                >
                    <!-- Visual: Chip bag with air -->
                    <div
                        class="relative w-32 h-40 bg-slate-200 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-end pb-4 overflow-hidden shadow-xl transform rotate-3"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[60%] bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-200/50 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center"
                        >
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:weather-windy"
                                class="w-12 h-12 text-sky-600/50 animate-pulse"
                            />
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-[40%] bg-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center"
                        >
                            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-amber-900">PATATAS</span>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-2 right-2 bg-red-600 text-white text-[8px] font-bold px-1 rounded"
                        >
                            NUEVO FORMATO
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur text-white text-xs font-mono p-2 rounded border border-white/10"
                    >
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                            <Icon name="mdi:food-apple" class="w-3 h-3 text-amber-400" /> 243g (Antes
                            295g)
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-pink-400 font-bold flex items-center gap-1">
                            <Icon name="mdi:arrow-up-bold" class="w-3 h-3" /> Precio: +15%
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3 italic">
                    "Te venden aire a precio de comida."
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    El caso de las <strong>patatas fritas</strong> es de libro: bajaron de 295g a 275g,
                    y luego a 243g, mientras subían el precio. Las asociaciones de consumidores han denunciado
                    reducciones de hasta el 17% en productos de primeras marcas.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://facua.org/noticias/doce-productos-donde-facua-ha-detectado-reduflacion-reducen-la-cantidad-ademas-de-subir-el-precio/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-xs text-pink-400 hover:underline mt-2 block opacity-70 hover:opacity-100"
                    >Fuente: Estudio FACUA (12 productos detectados)</a
                >

                <button
                    data-share-btn
                    data-share-text="¿Te has dado cuenta de que las bolsas de patatas son 60% aire? Se llama Reduflación: te venden aire a precio de comida."
                    class="absolute bottom-4 right-6 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:share-variant" class="w-4 h-4" />
                    Compartir
                </button>
            </article>

            <!-- 2. Cutreflación -->
            <article
                class="group relative bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-800 hover:border-amber-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-2xl overflow-visible"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-6 -right-2 md:-right-6 -rotate-6 bg-amber-600 text-white font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(217,119,6,0.4)] transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform z-20 border-2 border-amber-400"
                >
                    PEOR POR LO MISMO
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-lg">
                        <Icon name="mdi:emoticon-poop" class="w-8 h-8" />
                    </div>
                    Cutreflación
                </h3>

                <div
                    class="h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-8 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-700 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.2)] transition-shadow"
                >
                    <!-- Visual: Ingredients label -->
                    <div
                        class="p-6 bg-white text-black font-mono text-xs -rotate-2 shadow-xl max-w-[240px] rounded relative"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 bg-yellow-400 text-black font-bold px-2 py-1 text-[10px] shadow-sm rotate-12"
                        >
                            RECETA MEJORADA
                        </div>
                        <div class="border-b-2 border-black pb-2 mb-2 font-black text-sm">
                            INGREDIENTES:
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <div
                                class="flex justify-between items-center opacity-40 line-through decoration-red-500 decoration-2"
                            >
                                <span>Aceite de Girasol</span>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex justify-between items-center text-green-700 font-bold bg-green-100 px-1 -mx-1 rounded"
                            >
                                <span>Grasa de Palma/Mix</span>
                                <Icon name="mdi:alert-circle" class="w-3 h-3" />
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex justify-between items-center opacity-40 line-through decoration-red-500 decoration-2"
                            >
                                <span>Mantequilla</span>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex justify-between items-center text-green-700 font-bold bg-green-100 px-1 -mx-1 rounded"
                            >
                                <span>Aceites Vegetales</span>
                                <Icon name="mdi:flask" class="w-3 h-3" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3 italic">
                    "Te cambian los ingredientes buenos por sucedáneos baratos."
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Tras la crisis de Ucrania, muchas marcas sustituyeron el aceite de girasol por <strong
                        >aceites de palma o mezclas vegetales</strong
                    > en mayonesas, galletas y salsas. El problema: la etiqueta "Sabor Tradicional" se
                    mantuvo, pero la calidad nutricional cayó en picado.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://www.npr.org/sections/money/2021/10/26/1048892388/meet-skimpflation-a-reason-inflation-is-worse-than-the-government-says-it-is"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-xs text-amber-400 hover:underline mt-2 block opacity-70 hover:opacity-100"
                    >Fuente: NPR (Origen del término Skimpflation)</a
                >

                <button
                    data-share-btn
                    data-share-text="¿La comida te sabe peor pero cuesta igual? Se llama Cutreflación: cambian ingredientes buenos por basura barata."
                    class="absolute bottom-4 right-6 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:share-variant" class="w-4 h-4" />
                    Compartir
                </button>
            </article>

            <!-- 3. Premiunización -->
            <article
                class="group relative bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-800 hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-2xl overflow-visible"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-6 -right-2 md:-right-6 rotate-6 bg-purple-600 text-white font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(147,51,234,0.4)] transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform z-20 border-2 border-purple-400"
                >
                    LA HUIDA HACIA ARRIBA
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg">
                        <Icon name="mdi:star-face" class="w-8 h-8" />
                    </div>
                    Premiunización
                </h3>

                <div
                    class="h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-8 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-700 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(168,85,247,0.2)] transition-shadow"
                >
                    <!-- Visual: Shelf -->
                    <div class="flex gap-4 items-end relative">
                        <div
                            class="w-24 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-purple-900 to-purple-600 rounded-t-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-2 border-2 border-purple-400 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(168,85,247,0.6)] z-10 transform scale-110"
                        >
                            <span class="text-[8px] tracking-widest text-purple-200 uppercase mb-1"
                                >Platinum</span
                            >
                            <span class="text-lg font-black text-white leading-none"
                                >ULTRA<br />PRO</span
                            >
                            <div
                                class="mt-2 bg-white text-purple-900 text-xs font-bold px-2 rounded-full"
                            >
                                12.99€
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-20 bg-gray-700 rounded-t-lg opacity-30 flex flex-col items-center justify-center border border-gray-600 grayscale blur-[1px]"
                        >
                            <span class="text-[8px] text-gray-400">Básico</span>
                            <div
                                class="mt-1 bg-gray-600 text-gray-400 text-[8px] px-1 rounded line-through"
                            >
                                2.99€
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="absolute -bottom-2 left-28 text-red-500 font-bold text-xs rotate-12"
                        >
                            ¡AGOTADO!
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3 italic">
                    "Eliminan la gama básica para obligarte a comprar la gama de lujo."
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    La fiebre "High Protein" ha desplazado a los yogures básicos. El detergente en
                    polvo (más barato y eficiente) desaparece de los lineales para dejar sitio a las
                    "Cápsulas 3 en 1" que cuestan el triple por lavado.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://www.cesce.es/es/w/asesores-de-pymes/premiumizacion-optimizacion"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-xs text-purple-400 hover:underline mt-2 block opacity-70 hover:opacity-100"
                    >Fuente: CESCE (Estrategia de Premiumización)</a
                >

                <button
                    data-share-btn
                    data-share-text="¿Ya no encuentras la versión barata de nada? Se llama Premiunización: eliminan lo básico para obligarte a pagar el lujo."
                    class="absolute bottom-4 right-6 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:share-variant" class="w-4 h-4" />
                    Compartir
                </button>
            </article>

            <!-- 4. Inflación Sombra -->
            <article
                class="group relative bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-slate-800 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-2xl overflow-visible"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-6 -right-2 md:-right-6 -rotate-12 bg-cyan-600 text-white font-black px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(8,145,178,0.4)] transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform z-20 border-2 border-cyan-400"
                >
                    TÚ ERES EL EMPLEADO
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="p-2 bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-lg">
                        <Icon name="mdi:robot-dead" class="w-8 h-8" />
                    </div>
                    Inflación Sombra
                </h3>

                <div
                    class="h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 rounded-2xl mb-8 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-700 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(34,211,238,0.2)] transition-shadow"
                >
                    <!-- Visual: Self checkout -->
                    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div
                            class="w-32 h-24 border-4 border-cyan-500/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 relative"
                        >
                            <Icon
                                name="mdi:barcode-scan"
                                class="w-16 h-16 text-cyan-500 animate-pulse"
                            />
                            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 w-full text-center">
                                <span
                                    class="bg-red-600 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rotate-6 inline-block shadow-lg border border-white/20"
                                    >ERROR: ESPERE ASISTENCIA</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-2 items-center">
                            <Icon name="mdi:account-hard-hat" class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-400" />
                            <span
                                class="text-xs text-slate-400 bg-slate-800 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-700"
                                >Tu Sueldo: 0€/hora</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3 italic">
                    "Trabajas gratis para el supermercado y encima pagas lo mismo."
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    La proliferación de cajas de autopago transfiere el coste laboral al cliente.
                    Estudios de mercado indican que el ahorro en personal (hasta un 40% en costes de
                    caja) no se repercute en una bajada de precios para el consumidor.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2018/oct/12/shadow-work-automation-tedious-jobs-oliver-burkeman"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="text-xs text-cyan-400 hover:underline mt-2 block opacity-70 hover:opacity-100"
                    >Fuente: The Guardian (Shadow Work & Automation)</a
                >

                <button
                    data-share-btn
                    data-share-text="¿Te toca cobrarte a ti mismo en el súper? Se llama Inflación Sombra: trabajas gratis y pagas lo mismo."
                    class="absolute bottom-4 right-6 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:share-variant" class="w-4 h-4" />
                    Compartir
                </button>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
